title: WALLPAPERS
creator: Smart Wallpaper Art
informationText: Wallpaper images shown in this app are artistic works and you as a user need the permission of the owner (David Teboul) if you want to perform certain acts, such as copying the image or sharing it on the internet. Always contact the owner of the images first.

socialmedia.bioInfo: You can visit Smart Wallpaper Art on Twitter and Telegram where you can find more great hand made wallpapers.
